<div style="font-size:8px;color:var(--g4);line-height:1.5">Shift change is the most rushed handoff point. Stores with high flag rates correlate to understaffed PM shifts. Recommend: mandate 15-min overlap between shifts for routine completion. 6 stores account for 68% of shift-change flags — target coaching there first.</div>
