<div style="font-size:8px;color:var(--g4);line-height:1.5">Before GPS: 22 off-site completions per month. After: 6 per month. Remaining 6 are from stores with poor cell signal — consider Wi-Fi verification fallback. GPS alone is the single highest-ROI anti-falsification measure deployed.</div>
