<div style="font-size:7px;color:var(--g2);line-height:1.5">This is <b style="color:var(--w)">presentation-ready today</b>. The supplier scorecard is the kind of tool CFOs and COOs reference in quarterly reviews. The receiving compliance tie-in to Line Item #105 connects supply chain directly to food safety scores — a story no competitor is telling. Recommend framing this as: "We can predict which suppliers will cause our next critical finding before it happens."</div>
