<div style="font-size:7px;color:var(--g2);line-height:1.5">Compared to FoodLogiQ, Arrowstream, and BlueCart supply chain dashboards, this <b style="color:var(--w)">matches or exceeds visual quality</b>. The integration of supply chain data with food safety scoring (Line Item #105) is a UX pattern <b style="color:var(--w)">none of those platforms offer</b> — they treat supply chain and compliance as separate worlds. This is the differentiator.</div>
